def_cn: 常春藤联合会(指美国东北部八所名牌大学)
def_en: The Ivy League is a group of eight universities in the north-eastern part of the United States, which have high academic and social status.

def_cn: (时尚、态度)典型常春藤大学生的
def_en: You use Ivy League to describe fashions and attitudes typical of students at Ivy League universities.
